A magical laboratory
The mage who could answer questions about the artiefact - His - has taken up residence in his laboratory and has not appeared in town for a long time. You can try to pay the mage a visit; apparently the lab is not far from the city.
#subobj 1
Find the entrance to the lab
His magic lab is located slightly east of town. You may encounter wild animals along the way.
#subobj 2
Disable the trap
Apparently the lab's host is not very hospitable - there's a magic trap set up at the entrance!
#subobj 3
Kill the guardian tigers
In addition to magical defenses, the lab is also protected by specially trained tigers.
#subobj 4
Enter the lab
The way is clear! It's time to get your questions answered.
